    "Asemblerski jezici i asemblersko programiranje: potprogram, makro i stek.":{"en": "Assembly languages and assembly programming: subroutine, macro, and stack.", "de": "Assemblersprachen und Assembler-Programmierung: Unterprogramm, Makro und Stack.", "fr": "Langages assembleur et programmation assembleur : sous-programme, macro et pile.", "es": "Lenguajes ensamblador y programación en ensamblador: subrutina, macro y pila.", "it": "Linguaggi assembly e programmazione in assembly: sottoprogramma, macro e stack.", "ru": "Языки ассемблера и программирование на ассемблере: подпрограмма, макрос и стек.", "pt": "Linguagens assembly e programação em assembly: sub-rotina, macro e pilha."},
