    "Besplatan SPICE: crtanje šeme, direktive .tran/.ac/.dc/.step/.meas, izvori i waveform viewer.":{"en": "Free SPICE: schematic drawing, .tran/.ac/.dc/.step/.meas directives, sources, and a waveform viewer.", "de": "Kostenloses SPICE: Schaltplanzeichnung, .tran/.ac/.dc/.step/.meas-Direktiven, Quellen und Waveform-Viewer.", "fr": "SPICE gratuit : dessin du schéma, directives .tran/.ac/.dc/.step/.meas, sources et visualiseur de courbes.", "es": "SPICE gratuito: dibujo del esquemático, directivas .tran/.ac/.dc/.step/.meas, fuentes y visor de formas de onda.", "it": "SPICE gratuito: disegno dello schema, direttive .tran/.ac/.dc/.step/.meas, sorgenti e waveform viewer.", "ru": "Бесплатный SPICE: рисование схемы, директивы .tran/.ac/.dc/.step/.meas, источники и просмотрщик осциллограмм.", "pt": "SPICE gratuito: desenho do esquemático, diretivas .tran/.ac/.dc/.step/.meas, fontes e visualizador de formas de onda."},
