    "Za decimale koristi double.":{"en": "For decimals, use double.", "de": "Für Dezimalzahlen verwende double.", "fr": "Pour les décimaux, utilise double.", "es": "Para decimales, usa double.", "it": "Per i decimali, usa double.", "ru": "Для дробных чисел используй double.", "pt": "Para decimais, usa double."},
