    "Otpornost se menja linearno preko temperaturnog koeficijenta TC (ppm/°C):":{"en": "Resistance changes linearly through the temperature coefficient TC (ppm/°C):", "de": "Der Widerstand ändert sich linear über den Temperaturkoeffizienten TC (ppm/°C):", "fr": "La résistance varie linéairement via le coefficient de température TC (ppm/°C) :", "es": "La resistencia cambia linealmente a través del coeficiente de temperatura TC (ppm/°C):", "it": "La resistenza cambia linearmente tramite il coefficiente di temperatura TC (ppm/°C):", "ru": "Сопротивление меняется линейно через температурный коэффициент TC (ppm/°C):", "pt": "A resistência muda linearmente através do coeficiente de temperatura TC (ppm/°C):"},
