    "Postavljaš komponente (R, C, L, dioda, tranzistor, izvor), povezuješ":{"en": "You place components (R, C, L, diode, transistor, source), you connect", "de": "Du platzierst Bauteile (R, C, L, Diode, Transistor, Quelle), verbindest", "fr": "Tu places des composants (R, C, L, diode, transistor, source), tu relies", "es": "Colocas componentes (R, C, L, diodo, transistor, fuente), conectas", "it": "Posizioni componenti (R, C, L, diodo, transistor, sorgente), colleghi", "ru": "Ты размещаешь компоненты (R, C, L, диод, транзистор, источник), соединяешь", "pt": "Você posiciona componentes (R, C, L, diodo, transistor, fonte), conecta"},
