    "Rešenje:   SAIFI = 3.8447  ·  SAIDI = 28.2213  ·  ENS = 358700  ·  ŠTETA = 3.480.800":{"en": "Solution:   SAIFI = 3.8447  ·  SAIDI = 28.2213  ·  ENS = 358700  ·  DAMAGE = 3.480.800", "de": "Lösung:   SAIFI = 3.8447  ·  SAIDI = 28.2213  ·  ENS = 358700  ·  SCHADEN = 3.480.800", "fr": "Solution :   SAIFI = 3.8447  ·  SAIDI = 28.2213  ·  ENS = 358700  ·  DOMMAGE = 3.480.800", "es": "Solución:   SAIFI = 3.8447  ·  SAIDI = 28.2213  ·  ENS = 358700  ·  DAÑO = 3.480.800", "it": "Soluzione:   SAIFI = 3.8447  ·  SAIDI = 28.2213  ·  ENS = 358700  ·  DANNO = 3.480.800", "ru": "Решение:   SAIFI = 3.8447  ·  SAIDI = 28.2213  ·  ENS = 358700  ·  УЩЕРБ = 3.480.800", "pt": "Solução:   SAIFI = 3.8447  ·  SAIDI = 28.2213  ·  ENS = 358700  ·  DANO = 3.480.800"},
