    "Iz inostranstva? Unesi broj sa pozivnim, npr. +30 69\u2026":{en:"From abroad? Enter your number with the country code, e.g. +30 69\u2026",de:"Aus dem Ausland? Nummer mit L\u00e4ndervorwahl eingeben, z. B. +30 69\u2026",fr:"De l'\u00e9tranger ? Saisis ton num\u00e9ro avec l'indicatif, ex. +30 69\u2026",es:"\u00bfDesde el extranjero? Introduce el n\u00famero con prefijo, p. ej. +30 69\u2026",it:"Dall'estero? Inserisci il numero con il prefisso, es. +30 69\u2026",ru:"\u0418\u0437-\u0437\u0430 \u0433\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0446\u044b? \u0412\u0432\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u0435 \u043d\u043e\u043c\u0435\u0440 \u0441 \u043a\u043e\u0434\u043e\u043c \u0441\u0442\u0440\u0430\u043d\u044b, \u043d\u0430\u043f\u0440. +30 69\u2026",pt:"Do estrangeiro? Introduz o n\u00famero com indicativo, ex. +30 69\u2026"},
